title: Repaired Rigmar SM Karaoke CDG+MP3
description: RESEED repaired archive. Sorry but I did not upload the correct file type, but the original Ots DJ Pro format. This has been corrected and the archive remade. Once again I am very sorry about that. Thanks to the peers who took the trouble to contact me. Song master are a Hungarian Music Service who use the Zoom backing tracks to master an interesting sub collection of there back catalogue with some pretty hard to get tracks on offer as well. http://www.songmasters.hu/ Audio is 128 or better on the newer tracks. CDG+MP3 in a single RAR Archive, over 200 songs with text track list outside the main Archive. Rigmar Radio - Rockin' the Free World since 1967
